{"total":23,"pageSize":8,"pageCount":3,"data":[{"title":"copy-virtual-ubuntu","slug":"copy-virtual-ubuntu","date":"2019-11-13T10:47:21.000Z","updated":"2019-11-13T10:59:45.132Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/copy-virtual-ubuntu.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\"><a href=\"#解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0\"></a>解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡<code>eth0</code></h1><h2 id=\"背景\"><a href=\"#背景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"背景\"></a>背景</h2><p>最近在学习Linux程序设计及驱动相关知识，买了宝华老师的书，但是在把baohua_linux复制到本地之后，从虚拟机进入ifconfig，只有lo网络，没有其他网卡，虚拟机的网络适配器设置为NAT模式。</p>\n<h2 id=\"原因\"><a href=\"#原因\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原因\"></a>原因</h2><ol>\n<li><p><code>UUID</code>为机器标识码，保证对同一时空的所有机器唯一。虚拟机同样会有一个UUID，而且这个UUID是唯一的。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>虚拟机的<code>UUID</code>一般和虚拟机配置文件的位置和物理主机有关。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>虚拟机移动时不需要改变<code>UUID</code>.复制时<code>UUID</code>对应的<code>Mac</code>地址改变。导致eth0设备装载的配置与默认不一致。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>同时，<code>70-persistent-net.rules文件</code>中记录了<code>MAC</code>以及<code>eth0</code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"解决办法\"><a href=\"#解决办法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决办法\"></a>解决办法</h2><ul>\n<li><p>生成<code>70-persistent-net.rules文件</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果系统中已有<code>/etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules</code>,删除，重启会自动生成</li>\n<li><p>如没有，手动生成</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><code>export MATCHADDR=”00:f1:f3:1a:f0:05”</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>export INTERFACE=eth0</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>sudo /lib/udev/write_net_rules</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>查看系统的网卡 <code>lspci | grep Eth*</code> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>显示为<code>Ethernet controller: Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. [AMD] 79c970 [PCnet32 LANCE] (rev 10)</code></li>\n<li>打开VMware 虚拟机配置 (.vmx)，在其中添加一行ethernet0.virtualDev = “e1000”</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#参考链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考链接\"></a>参考链接</h2><ul>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/five0918/article/details/72782531\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">本文直接参考</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/gw85047034/article/details/50978490\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">手动生成<code>eth0</code>以及<code>mac</code>配置文件</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><a href=\"https://blog.51cto.com/bfe99/900977\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">虚拟机移动后<code>uuid</code>不匹配问题</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"解决复制的虚拟机无法识别网卡eth0背景最近在学习Linux程序设计及驱动相关知识，买了宝华老师的书，但是在把baohua_linux复制到本地之后，从虚拟机进入ifconfig，只有lo网络，没有其他网卡，虚拟机的网络适配器设置为NAT模式。原因UUID为机器标识码，保证对同一","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"vmware","slug":"vmware","count":1,"path":"api/tags/vmware.json"},{"name":"network","slug":"network","count":1,"path":"api/tags/network.json"}]},{"title":"build-hello-module-in-linux","slug":"build-hello-module-in-linux","date":"2019-11-13T02:49:12.000Z","updated":"2019-11-13T08:37:32.798Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/build-hello-module-in-linux.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/1zoMHxPZeOBiFSr.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"编译简单的linux内核模块\"><a href=\"#编译简单的linux内核模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译简单的linux内核模块\"></a>编译简单的<code>linux</code>内核模块</h1><h2 id=\"hello-c\"><a href=\"#hello-c\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hello.c\"></a><code>hello.c</code></h2><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"C\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/*</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * a simple kernel module: hello</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Copyright (C) 2014 Barry Song  (baohua@kernel.org)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> *</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> * Licensed under GPLv2 or later.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"> */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/init.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&lt;linux/module.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> __<span class=\"function\">init <span class=\"title\">hello_init</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tprintk(KERN_INFO <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World in hjl's linux\\n\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">module_init(hello_init);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> __<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"built_in\">exit</span> <span class=\"title\">hello_exit</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">void</span>)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tprintk(KERN_INFO <span class=\"string\">\"Hello World exit byebye\\n \"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">module_exit(hello_exit);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_AUTHOR(<span class=\"string\">\"Hu Jinlei &lt;hjl2016060203025@std.uestc.edu.cn&gt;\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_LICENSE(<span class=\"string\">\"GPL v2\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_DESCRIPTION(<span class=\"string\">\"A simple Hello World Module\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">MODULE_ALIAS(<span class=\"string\">\"a simplest module\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ol>\n<li>编译</li>\n<li><code>insmod ./hello.ko</code>加载</li>\n<li><code>rmmod hello</code>卸载</li>\n<li><code>lsmod</code>显示加载的模块</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/1zoMHxPZeOBiFSr.jpg\" alt=\"03-arm-linux-module.jpg\"></p>\n","text":"编译简单的linux内核模块hello.c1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>11<br>12<br>13<br>14<br>15<br>16<br>17<br>18<br>19<br>20<br>21<br>22","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"module","slug":"module","count":1,"path":"api/tags/module.json"}]},{"title":"config-kernel-arm","slug":"config-kernel-arm","date":"2019-11-13T02:34:34.000Z","updated":"2019-11-13T02:41:29.189Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/config-kernel-arm.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"linux-内核的配置\"><a href=\"#linux-内核的配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux 内核的配置\"></a><code>linux</code> 内核的配置</h1><h2 id=\"四种打开方式\"><a href=\"#四种打开方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四种打开方式\"></a>四种打开方式</h2><ul>\n<li><p><code>make config</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make menuconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make xconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>make gconfig</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><code>menuconfig</code> 如下所示</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg\" alt=\"01-arm-linux-qemu-lcd.jpg\"></p>\n","text":"linux 内核的配置四种打开方式make configmake menuconfigmake xconfigmake gconfigmenuconfig 如下所示 [Figure] ","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":2,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"}]},{"title":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","slug":"build-linux-kenel-in-qumu","date":"2019-11-13T01:54:56.000Z","updated":"2019-11-13T02:09:00.052Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/build-linux-kenel-in-qumu.json","excerpt":"","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"><a href=\"#在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核\"></a>在<code>QEMU</code>中运行编译的<code>Linux</code>内核</h1><h2 id=\"内核编译脚本-build-sh\"><a href=\"#内核编译脚本-build-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"内核编译脚本 build.sh\"></a>内核编译脚本 <code>build.sh</code></h2><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export ARCH=arm</span><br><span class=\"line\">export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extra</span><br><span class=\"line\">export CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi-</span><br><span class=\"line\">make LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</span><br><span class=\"line\">make zImage -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make modules -j8</span><br><span class=\"line\">make dtbs</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/zImage extra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp arch/arm/boot/dts/*ca9.dtb\textra/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cp .config extra/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li><p>默认的内核配置文件为 <code>LDDD3_vexpress_defconfig</code>.上述脚本会将自动编译好的<code>zImage,dtbs</code>复制到<code>extra</code>目录中</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>extra</code>目录下的vexpress是一张虚拟的SD卡，作为<em>根文件系统</em>的存放介质。它能以<code>loop</code>形式被挂载<code>mount</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"编译模块的脚本-module-sh\"><a href=\"#编译模块的脚本-module-sh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编译模块的脚本 module.sh\"></a>编译模块的脚本 <code>module.sh</code></h2><div class=\"highlight-wrap\"autocomplete=\"off\" autocorrect=\"off\" autocapitalize=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\" contenteditable=\"true\"data-rel=\"SHELL\"><figure class=\"iseeu highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo mount -o loop,offset=$((2048*512)) extra/vexpress.img extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo make ARCH=arm CROSS_COMPILE=arm-linux-gnueabi- modules_install INSTALL_MOD_PATH=extra/img</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo umount extra/img</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>\n<ul>\n<li>它会自动编译内核模块并安装到<code>vexprees.img</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"启动带LCD的ARM-Linux内核\"><a href=\"#启动带LCD的ARM-Linux内核\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启动带LCD的ARM Linux内核\"></a>启动带<code>LCD</code>的<code>ARM Linux</code>内核</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/11/13/RV1HtyCN2Y3OPsW.jpg\" alt=\"01-arm-linux-qemu-lcd.jpg\"></p>\n","text":"在QEMU中运行编译的Linux内核内核编译脚本 build.sh1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>export ARCH=arm<br>export EXTRADIR=$&#123;PWD&#125;/extr","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"linux","slug":"linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/linux.json"},{"name":"drivers","slug":"drivers","count":2,"path":"api/tags/drivers.json"}]},{"title":"funds","slug":"funds","date":"2019-03-29T15:17:18.000Z","updated":"2019-03-29T16:03:43.000Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/funds.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"从零开始的基金之路\"><a href=\"#从零开始的基金之路\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"从零开始的基金之路\"></a>从零开始的基金之路</h1><p>人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。</p>\n<h2 id=\"根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"><a href=\"#根本准则-：-追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格\"></a>根本准则 ： <code>追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格</code></h2><p>若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"text":"从零开始的基金之路人生有哲学，而哲学是指导思考的元科学。同样的，基金的操作也<br>应该有思考反思遵循的哲学。根本准则 ： 追求持有成本尽可能的低于现有价格若总的持有价格小于当前，且这个差值的累积之和，那么就可以使得<br>基金增持。此路缘何当作养成游戏的娱乐养成储蓄的习惯保持学","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"基金","slug":"基金","count":1,"path":"api/tags/基金.json"}]},{"title":"auto-google-translation","slug":"auto-google-translation","date":"2019-02-15T01:57:53.000Z","updated":"2019-02-15T02:08:28.118Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/auto-google-translation.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"字幕也疯狂\"><a href=\"#字幕也疯狂\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"字幕也疯狂\"></a>字幕也疯狂</h1><p><code>观曲千首 不如操琴一曲</code> 试着做一个勤劳的字幕组小员工~</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s28051018.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100%\"></p>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img1.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s28051018.jpg","content":null,"text":"字幕也疯狂观曲千首 不如操琴一曲 试着做一个勤劳的字幕组小员工~ [Figure] Bili链接","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":5,"path":"api/tags/python.json"},{"name":"script","slug":"script","count":1,"path":"api/tags/script.json"}]},{"title":"some_tools_in_computer","slug":"some-tools-in-computer","date":"2019-02-14T04:29:06.000Z","updated":"2019-02-15T02:12:39.516Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/some-tools-in-computer.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"龙套角色也精彩\"><a href=\"#龙套角色也精彩\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"龙套角色也精彩\"></a>龙套角色也精彩</h1><p>这是学习<a href=\"\">操作系统</a>时总结的一些编程开发工具，虽然这些并不是实实在在的<br>生产力开发工具，当在实际应用中，缺少他们却是万万不能的。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/02/14/5c64efab4c2e4.jpg\" width=\"60%\" height=\"60%\"><br>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/02/14/5c64efab4c2e4.jpg","content":null,"text":"龙套角色也精彩这是学习操作系统时总结的一些编程开发工具，虽然这些并不是实实在在的<br>生产力开发工具，当在实际应用中，缺少他们却是万万不能的。 [Figure] 参考链接dd参考页","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"tools","slug":"tools","count":1,"path":"api/tags/tools.json"}]},{"title":"latency-in-programmar","slug":"latency-in-programmar","date":"2019-02-11T11:47:46.000Z","updated":"2019-02-11T11:54:22.587Z","comments":true,"pin":null,"path":"api/articles/latency-in-programmar.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"Latency-Comparison-Numbers-2012\"><a href=\"#Latency-Comparison-Numbers-2012\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Latency Comparison Numbers (~2012)\"></a>Latency Comparison Numbers (~2012)</h1><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/02/11/5c6161e41f278.jpg\" width=\"40%\" height=\"40%\"></p>","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.loli.net/2019/02/11/5c6161e41f278.jpg","content":null,"text":"Latency Comparison Numbers (~2012) [Figure] NameL1 cache reference0.5nsBranch mispredict5nsL2 cachereference7ns14x L1 cacheMutex lock/unlock","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"tips","slug":"tips","count":1,"path":"api/tags/tips.json"}]}]}